 {"id":"coding_agent_session_search-2dccg","title":"EPIC: FrankenTUI visual polish — close the gap with ratatui v0.1.64","description":"## Background

The FrankenTUI (ftui) migration was an architectural triumph: Elm architecture, virtual lists, responsive breakpoints, degradation-aware rendering, command palette, 7-tab inspector cockpit, and more. But the install scripts are still pinned to v0.1.64 (the last ratatui build) because the ftui version looks visibly worse despite being technically superior.

## Root Cause Analysis (2026-02-08)

A deep audit of app.rs (~22K lines), style_system.rs (~1.5K lines), components/theme.rs, and all test snapshots revealed these categories of issue:

1. **Half-wired style system**: 5 of 24 semantic style tokens (STYLE_PILL_ACTIVE, STYLE_TAB_ACTIVE, STYLE_TAB_INACTIVE, STYLE_KBD_KEY, STYLE_KBD_DESC) are defined in the stylesheet but NEVER referenced in rendering code. They were designed for visual polish but nobody connected the wires.

2. **Theme-blind markdown**: The detail pane creates `MarkdownRenderer::new(MarkdownTheme::default())` at app.rs:4327 and :4390, ignoring the active theme preset (Dark/Light/Catppuccin/Dracula/Nord/HighContrast). Code blocks, headers, bold text all render in hardcoded default colors that clash with the surrounding UI.

3. **Incomplete role gutter port**: Only STYLE_ROLE_GUTTER_ASSISTANT is used (app.rs:4214). User, tool, and system gutter styles are defined but never rendered. The old ratatui version had per-role colored gutters throughout.

4. **Filter pills rendered as flat text**: Pills use STYLE_TEXT_PRIMARY (just foreground color) instead of STYLE_PILL_ACTIVE (which has a background). No visual "chip" affordance — just a text string.

5. **Unstyled detail find bar**: No border, no background, no focus indicator at app.rs:4895-4910. Blends into content above.

6. **Possibly over-aggressive degradation**: The frame budget thresholds may strip styling even on capable terminals.

7. **Minimal test fixtures**: Snapshot tests use bare-minimum synthetic data that does not exercise the visual richness (no agent icons, no score bars, no snippets in the snapshots).

8. **Stale README**: Screenshots show the old ratatui version, install scripts pinned to v0.1.64.

## Success Criteria

- All 24 style tokens used in rendering code (zero dead tokens)
- Markdown in detail pane respects active theme preset
- Filter pills visually distinct as chips/badges
- Detail find bar has visible border/background
- All 4 role gutters render correctly
- Snapshot tests exercise full visual richness
- Screenshots updated to show ftui version
- Install scripts unpinned from v0.1.64
- `cargo clippy --all-targets -- -D warnings` clean throughout

## Key Files

- src/ui/app.rs (main rendering, ~22K lines)
- src/ui/style_system.rs (style tokens + stylesheet builder)
- src/ui/components/theme.rs (color palette, agent tints)
- src/ui/ftui_adapter.rs (central ftui import hub)
- tests/snapshots/*.snap (rendering baselines)
- README.md (screenshots, install script version)
- install.sh / install.ps1 (version pin)","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-02-08T19:29:41.488509398Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-09T02:50:16.271081017Z","closed_at":"2026-02-09T02:50:16.271056401Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"comments":[{"id":248,"issue_id":"coding_agent_session_search-2dccg","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"## Execution Architecture (Self-Contained)

