- Epic closure requires an auditable go/no-go report (Track G.5) with evidence links.","created_at":"2026-02-08T19:41:07Z"},{"id":269,"issue_id":"coding_agent_session_search-2dccg","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"## Plan-Space Optimization Revision (2026-02-08)

This epic was revised to remove execution ambiguity and expand scope without feature loss.

